SELECT experiment_name, outcome_description FROM experiments JOIN experiment_outcomes ON experiments.experiment_id = experiment_outcomes.experiment_id JOIN outcomes ON experiment_outcomes.outcome_id = outcomes.outcome_id;

SELECT experiment_name, variable_name, variable_description FROM experiments JOIN experiment_variables ON experiments.experiment_id = experiment_variables.experiment_id JOIN variables ON experiment_variables.variable_id = variables.variable_id;
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date FROM experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;

SELECT e.experiment_name, v.variable_name, o.outcome_description FROM experiments e JOIN experiment_variables ev ON e.experiment_id = ev.experiment_id JOIN variables v ON ev.variable_id = v.variable_id JOIN experiment_outcomes eo ON e.experiment_id = eo.experiment_id JOIN outcomes o ON eo.outcome_id = o.outcome_id WHERE e.experiment_date >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT e.experiment_name, v.variable_name, o.outcome_description FROM experiments e JOIN experiment_variables ev ON e.experiment_id = ev.experiment_id JOIN variables v ON ev.variable_id = v.variable_id JOIN experiment_outcomes eo ON e.experiment_id = eo.experiment_id JOIN outcomes o ON eo.outcome_id = o.outcome_id WHERE v.variable_name LIKE '%temperature%';

SELECT e.experiment_id, e.experiment_name, COUNT(ev.variable_id) AS num_variables FROM experiments e LEFT JOIN experiment_variables ev ON e.experiment_id = ev.experiment_id GROUP BY e.experiment_id ORDER BY num_variables DESC;
